# A [[sword]]-like [[tool]] used for [[cut]]ting large [[plant]]s with a [[chop]]ping motion.

A machete's blade usually 50 to 65 centimeters ([[cm]]) long, seven to ten centimeters wide, and up to three millimeters ([[mm]]) thick.

